posting_body: ['850 Calderon Apartments', 'show contact info', 'This is a quiet, well maintained community near major electronics and high tech industries.', 'The apartments have a perfect location in the Heart of Silicon Valley.', 'It is ultra convenient to freeways: 101, 85, 280 & 237.', 'Bedrooms: Studio', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Lease terms: 6-Month, 1 year', 'Pet policy: Cats allowed.', 'Office hours: Mon - Thu: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Fri - Sun: 8:30 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'If no one is available to answer the phone, PLEASE leave a message and someone WILL call you back.', 'If no response, please call Kathy, property manager, at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Amazing amenities and features', '·  Cat Friendly', '·  Individual Leases', '·  Onsite Management', '·  Refrigerator', '·  Oversized Closet', '·  Cable or Satellite Ready', '·  Assigned Parking', '·  Covered Parking', '·  Green Community', '·  Cats', '·  Heart of Silicon Valley', '·  Carpet', '·  Ceiling Fan', '·  Stove', '·  Near shopping', 'Professionally managed by Moseley Trust', 'Price is subject to change without prior notice', 'Photos in ad may not be of the actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.']
